I am so glad to be back to an area that I am happy to be be in!!!
  this trip has been a Feasco from the begining!
  left for the airport early, but he train I always take to the airport, stopped in a place called Chiba, about 45 min from the Airport, and I have to change trains, but miss the next train. so I have to wait an hour for he next one,  this makes me 45 minuets late for my 2 hours prior check in. thinking that I could get some sleep, what was I thinking? Children screaming during for almost the entire flight!
  San Jose:  this place has to have the worst customs in the nation! They had 3 lines open for about 350 people, about 75% of us were Citizens or Residents, and only 1 of the 3 lines were for us. This resulted in a hour wai before they opened up another line for us. after all that time waiting it takes me about 30 seconds to go through customs. 
  I get something to eat and wait in line to ceck in. Just As I get to the counter the guy gets a call from the ground crew and guess what...Planes Broke!!!  So I get redirected from my flight to St Lois to Chicago, I am only 2 hours behind schedule by this time, and now I am in Chi Town.
  Getting ready for the time to board the plane and they say that they say that they are rolling a new plane out from the hanger and it will take about a half hour for all the inspections before boarding will take place. we get to Columbus and I go to the Baggage claim, No baggage for me , no that would be convienient. so I fill out a claim check and go to the rental car counter to pick up my car, and I find out that they dont take Debit Cards.
 So I go to Budget and get one. Supposed to be at my moms house around Midnight, I get there @ 3:30. and of course all the doors are locked.
  the Day after next (saturday) I go Visit my father on the ther side of the state, no problems there but the next day I call my mother to tell thaat I have been invited to a family reunion my mother tells me that no morthan 10 after I had left her house Her mother had passsed away, and I was to visit her at the home the next day. so there are 2 days for the showings and then the Funeral. well due to the Death of my Grandmother I have to move my flight back a couple of days which I have to change plans with my sister and my friends for an Airport Pick up. well after a couple of days of not being able to get in touch to conirm changes to the plans, my sister calls about midnight and TOTALLY Pisses my step father... is ok I ate the fucker anyway, I mean this is the man who tought me how to hate! Well he goes of on how I gave her the # to the house, (even thougt my mother had asked me to do this a while ago!) and fro making long-distance calls, (I had asked permission first). So Asshole states that 'I have to pack and be gone as soon as the funerla is over and If I ever come to the house there again he'll kill me' And now you know why I hate this slug of a Man! I get to Cali with out much of A hitch except for waiting at the airport and the is 'cause no one was expecting me. thankks to my GREAT Friend Amethyst Rose! well that is it for now! 

  Laters! F
